snippet.title: Juicy Realm Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Roguelite Twin-stick shooter Juicy Realm coming to Nintendo Switch on Nov 7th 2019!
Square off bizarre fruit monsters all across the world! Limited-time exclusive character and Boss Rush mode for Nintendo Switch!

Learn more about Juicy Realm:
Facebook: /JuicyRealm
Twitter: @JuicyRealm, @spacecangames, @XD_EN_Official
